name: r-groupedstats
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-groupedstats
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/groupedstats_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/groupedstats/groupedstats_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 94b05add92b487c2707d67cf2c6cb6787daf7baa91d229237d786d4045aba105

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base >=4.1
    - r-broomextra
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.0
    - r-effectsize
    - r-glue
    - r-haven
    - r-ipmisc
    - r-lme4
    - r-parameters
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-skimr
    - r-tibble
    - r-tidyr
  run:
    - r-base >=4.1
    - r-broomextra
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.0
    - r-effectsize
    - r-glue
    - r-haven
    - r-ipmisc
    - r-lme4
    - r-parameters
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-skimr
    - r-tibble
    - r-tidyr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('groupedstats')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('groupedstats')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://indrajeetpatil.github.io/groupedstats/, https://github.com/IndrajeetPatil/groupedstats/
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Collection of functions to run statistical tests across all combinations of multiple grouping variables.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
